org.eclipse.debug.core

Interface IMemoryBlockListener


  • public interface IMemoryBlockListener
    A memory block listener is notified of the addition and removal of memory blocks with the memory block manager. Listeners must register with the memory block manager for notification.

    Clients may implement this interface.

    Since:
    3.1

    • Method Summary
